      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Although climate change does not cause wildfires, it increases the risk
    of fire.


    Majority of wildfires are manmade, meaning they sprout from unattended
    campfires, discarded cigarettes, etc.


    Much of the environment has suffered
    from wildfires, especially animals who have lost their homes due to fires that
    could have been prevented.'
